{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 52,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الطُّورِ",
    "englishName": "At-Tur",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Mount",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 49,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4736,
        "text": "By oath of (mount) Tur.",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4737,
        "text": "And by oath of a passage, written –",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4738,
        "text": "On an open record.",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4739,
        "text": "And by oath of the Inhabited House.",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4740,
        "text": "And the lofty roof.",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4741,
        "text": "And the sea set aflame.",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4742,
        "text": "Indeed your Lord’s punishment will surely take place.",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4743,
        "text": "No one can avert it.",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4744,
        "text": "A day on which the heavens will shake with a visible shaking.",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4745,
        "text": "And the mountains will move with a visible movement.",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4746,
        "text": "So on that day, ruin is for those who deny.",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4747,
        "text": "Those who are playing in pursuits.",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4748,
        "text": "A day when they will be pushed, forcibly shoved towards the fire of hell.",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4749,
        "text": "“This is the fire, which you used to deny!”",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4750,
        "text": "“So is this magic, or are you unable to see?”",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4751,
        "text": "“Enter it – now whether you patiently bear it or are impatient – it is the same for you; for you is a recompense only for what you used to do.”",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4752,
        "text": "Indeed the pious are in Gardens and peace.",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4753,
        "text": "Delighted at the bestowal of their Lord; and their Lord has saved them from the fire.",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4754,
        "text": "“Eat and drink with pleasure, a reward for what you used to do.”",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4755,
        "text": "Reclining on thrones, in rows; and We have wedded them to maidens with gorgeous eyes.",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4756,
        "text": "And those who accepted faith, and whose descendants followed them with faith – We have joined their descendants with them, and have not reduced anything for them from their deeds; every soul is trapped in its own deeds.",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4757,
        "text": "And We aided them with fruit and meat, whatever they desire.",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4758,
        "text": "In it, they accept cups from each other, in which is neither any lewdness nor any sin.",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4759,
        "text": "And their boy servants shall go around them, as if they were pearls, safely hidden.",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4760,
        "text": "And one of them turned towards the other, questioning.",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4761,
        "text": "Saying, “Indeed before this, we were in our houses, worried.”",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4762,
        "text": "“So Allah did us a great favour, and saved us from the punishment of the flame.”",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4763,
        "text": "“Indeed we used to worship Him in our previous life; indeed He only is the Benign, the Most Merciful.”",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4764,
        "text": "Therefore (O dear Prophet Mohammed – peace and blessings be upon him), enlighten, for by the munificence of your Lord, you are neither a soothsayer nor a madman.",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4765,
        "text": "Or they allege, “He is a poet – we await a calamity of the times to befall him.”",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4766,
        "text": "Proclaim, “Go on waiting – I too am waiting along with you.”",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4767,
        "text": "Is this what their senses tell them, or are they a rebellious people?",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4768,
        "text": "What! They say, “He has invented the Qur'an”? Rather they do not have faith.",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4769,
        "text": "So let them bring a single discourse like it, if they are truthful.",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4770,
        "text": "Have they not been created from some source, or are they themselves the creators?",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4771,
        "text": "Or did they create the heavens and the earth? Rather they are not certain.",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4772,
        "text": "Or do they have the treasures of your Lord, or are they the authority?",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4773,
        "text": "Or do they have any stairs, climbing upon which they eavesdrop? So their eavesdropper should bring some clear proof!",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4774,
        "text": "What! The daughters for Him, and the sons for you?",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4775,
        "text": "Or do you (O dear Prophet Mohammed – peace and blessings be upon him) ask any fee from them, so they are burdened with the penalty?",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4776,
        "text": "Or is the hidden with them, by which they pass judgements?",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4777,
        "text": "Or are they planning a conspiracy? So the conspiracy will befall only upon the disbelievers.",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4778,
        "text": "Or do they have a God besides Allah? Purity is to Allah from their ascribing of partners to Him.",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4779,
        "text": "And were they to see a portion of the sky falling, they will say, “It is a heap of clouds.”",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4780,
        "text": "Therefore leave them, until they confront their day, in which they will be stunned.",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4781,
        "text": "A day on which their scheming will not benefit them at all, nor will they be helped.",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4782,
        "text": "And indeed for the unjust is another punishment before this, but most of them do not know. (Punishment in the grave is proven by this verse.)",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4783,
        "text": "And be patient upon your Lord’s command, (O dear Prophet Mohammed – peace and blessings be upon him), for you are indeed in Our sight; and proclaim the Purity of your Lord while praising Him, whenever you stand.",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4784,
        "text": "And proclaim His Purity during the night, and when the stars turn back.",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
